{"tid":1736552,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今晚一戰，我哋可以輸，但不可以認輸","createTime":"2019-11-18T18:17:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-18T18:28:25.000Z","uid":114354,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"659a31d345a292b1a792321875b93660858e70c5","tid":1736552,"uid":114354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T18:17:31.000Z","msg":"首先我要道歉，我係比較前嘅和理非，今晚七點幾喺某位置一路推下退下，去到十點幾都要閃。我知道仲有好多手足喺出面博緊命，萬事小心。<br />\n<br />\n今晚大家喺油尖旺同紅磡各自進行反包圍，雖然未夠攻入去，不過明顯班狗都忙著應戰，總算做到牽制作用同聲東擊西。見到大家齊心想推進，起碼俾poly手足知道所有手足都係齊上齊落，一個都不能少。<br />\n<br />\n我唔知道poly手足走咗幾多，亦唔知損失咗幾多手足，但係我知：我哋冇認輸！頂住啊各位！"},{"pid":"69018847b8007ca73ec4c755bfbbc1f3065a818a","tid":1736552,"uid":227441,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T18:20:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">因為polyu班on9仔囉 害撚死出面d手足 連d家長都俾人拉吖 跟住仲on99咁去自首 成班mk垃圾</span></span>"},{"pid":"fd280a78ea15a04262755cecc7255cb429d244d7","tid":1736552,"uid":338636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T18:21:30.000Z","msg":"[正能量撚]出去之前，希望你可以睇下呢個po<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1734559\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1734559</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"fc067b88a57a069af39a7a6e6cb6102fe72b572a","tid":1736552,"uid":338636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"69018847b8007ca73ec4c755bfbbc1f3065a818a","tid":1736552,"uid":227441,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T18:20:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">因為polyu班on9仔囉 害撚死出面d手足 連d家長都俾人拉吖 跟住仲on99咁去自首 成班mk垃圾</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T18:21:45.000Z","msg":"唔好再分化喇屌你"},{"pid":"693361152887a0c2a19bbcee16fae42c33725e54","tid":1736552,"uid":319824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"69018847b8007ca73ec4c755bfbbc1f3065a818a","tid":1736552,"uid":227441,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T18:20:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\